items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

items.checkin_comment: Salt from the umeboshi definitely noticeable in the overall mouthfeel. Light fruit. Aroma almost like a sour & actually the fruit plus salt gives hints of gose minus the sour. I imagine this does go well with ramen although sadly I have none to hand. #17
